It looks like the power pad uses the same controller pins as the Zapper.  I remember the satellite had a switch to select zapper/controller, but I don't know if that would work with all 4 ports.  I only know of one game that uses 2 zappers, that's Chiller.<br /><br />But yeah, it could definitely use 2 power pads, plugged straight in.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=10">Memblers</a> — Sat Sep 11, 2010 8:59 pm</p><hr />
